{"tid":1130682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【炒過百外賣仔】 Honestbee 大裁員！多名海外高層離職，香港部分業務即將暫停","createTime":"2019-04-29T08:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T10:06:46.000Z","uid":46049,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"93efb3251286188eb6129d1b972148e2d7d2e6e6","tid":1130682,"uid":46049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T08:18:54.000Z","msg":"朋友做緊Honestbee 收到風話香港會炒百幾個車手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n// Honestbee 暫停菲律賓業務、裁減員工，多個高管離職<br />\nHonestbee 是提供雜貨和食品配送服務的公司，近期卻面臨營收與人事方面的動盪。Honestbee 的總部位於新加坡，今年初，它暫停與新加坡的連鎖超商 NTUC FairPrice 的合作關係。<br />\n<br />\n近期，多個 Honestbee 的高管離職，並在印尼、<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港</span></span></strong>、泰國進行一波的裁員。Honestbee 發言人證實，有 6% 的員工受到影響。<br />\n<br />\nHonestbee 在菲律賓的業務目前也暫停，儘管菲律賓是 Honestbee 表現最好的市場，也是菲律賓 Android 和 iOS 上排名第一的食品飲料類別 APP。//<br />\n<a href=\"https://buzzorange.com/techorange/2019/04/24/honestbee-crisis/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com%2Ftechorange%2F2019%2F04%2F24%2Fhonestbee-crisis%2F&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9eSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=2372549b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://buzzorange.com/techorange/2019/04/24/honestbee-crisis/</a>"},{"pid":"3dffd6245963e38cd5450c5dc559630b58cb9967","tid":1130682,"uid":46049,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T08:25:06.000Z","msg":"有冇苦主出嚟講兩句<br />\nBTW 唔使多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www1.jobs.gov.hk/1/0/WebForm/Default.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.jobs.gov.hk%2F1%2F0%2FWebForm%2FDefault.aspx&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9eSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=c15d12a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www1.jobs.gov.hk/1/0/WebForm/Default.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"dd0d0b2e3beb4972c61e75cb223a083871b4669a","tid":1130682,"uid":18764,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyT